PrecisOrder (a) setting apart 1,913 hectares of land in Saskatchewan for the use and benefit of the BEARDY'S AND OKEMASIS BAND as Beardy's and Okemasis Indian Reserve No. 96 & 97-B or as an addition to its Reserve No. 96 & 97-A, and (b) consenting to the use by both SASKATCHEWAN POWER CORPORATION and the RURAL MUNICIPALITY OF BIG QUILL NO. 308 of their statutory powers to acquire EASEMENTS over some of those lands.
